FBIS4-15889 "drsov071_i_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 CENTRAL ASIA Kazakhstan Presidential Decree on Selling State Shares Presidential Decree on Selling State Shares LD1204180194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 1400 GMT 12 Apr 94 LD1204180194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network Kazakh BFN [Text] The president of the Republic of Kazakhstan has issued a decree on the use of money received by selling the state block of shares. The decree says in particular that money received from selling state blocks of shares of state joint-stock companies will be entered in their accounts and exclusively used for investment in their own production and technical upgrading. The text of the decree will be published in the press.
